org.anchoranalysis.io.manifest.directory

Class JobRootDirectory

  • Object
    • MutableDirectory
      • SubdirectoryBase
        • JobRootDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SequencedDirectory, WriteOperationRecorder

    public class JobRootDirectory
extends SubdirectoryBase
    The root directory for where outputs for a particular experiment occur.

    Subdirectories are recorded in this, but individual files are ignored.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
